was  totally  flooded  and  we  expect  to  be  back  at  business  on  Janu-
ary 17. Are we going to make it? I’m not sure. But I think we will 
and are going to make it because, it is important that we continue 
to  serve  this  state  and  this  region.  We  were  founded  to  serve  and 
