THE SOUTHEAST LOUISIANA BUSINESS COALITION 
Mr. DRENNEN. Yes, sir. Good morning, Mr. Chairman. I want to, 
like  everyone  else  here,  I  want  to  truly  thank  you  for  taking  the 
time  out  of  your  schedules  to  come  and  see  this  region.  I  grew  up, 
unlike  most  of  the  panel  people  today,  I  am  not  a  native  of  Lou-
isiana. I grew up in upstate New York. I moved to Louisiana, some 

