they’ve got to have a place to live. And other people will testify and 
work  with  you  on  how  we  do  the  rebuilding  of  our  neighborhoods 
and communities. But the ability to rebuild our jobs and to give our 
small businesses the ability to move forward is critical. 

Louisiana Rebirth, the Restoration of the Soul of America, a pro-
gram put together by many of the top national business leaders in 
our industry under the direction of our Lieutenant Governor has ef-
